    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0, "y": 18, "width": 24, "height": 4,
      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Geographic Distribution & Unique Visitors\n\nS3 metrics don't include geographic data. For visitor geography and unique IP counts, query the CloudFront access logs in Athena:\n\n```sql\nSELECT SUBSTR(x_edge_location, 1, 3) AS region, COUNT(*) AS requests, COUNT(DISTINCT c_ip) AS unique_visitors\nFROM cloudfront_logs\nWHERE cs_uri_stem LIKE '/aws%%2Bcoder%' OR cs_uri_stem LIKE '/aws+coder%'\nGROUP BY 1 ORDER BY requests DESC;\n```\n\nLogs location: `s3://aws-coder-microsites-logs/cloudfront-logs/`\n\n**Note:** S3 request metrics above show origin fetches only (CloudFront cache misses). Actual visitor traffic is higher when CloudFront serves from cache. For total visitor counts including cached hits, use the Athena queries on access logs."
      }
    }
  ]
